import {Container, Content, Row} from './styles';
import Input from './components/Input';
import Button from './components/Button';
function App() {
  return (
    <Container className="App">
      <Content>
       <Input/>
       <Row>
          <Button label="x"/>
          <Button label="/"/>
          <Button label="C"/>
          <Button label="X"/>
       </Row>
       <Row>
          <Button label="7"/>
          <Button label="8"/>
          <Button label="9"/>
          <Button label="-"/>
       </Row>
       <Row>
          <Button label="4"/>
          <Button label="5"/>
          <Button label="6"/>
          <Button label="+"/>
       </Row>
       <Row>
          <Button label="1"/>
          <Button label="2"/>
          <Button label="3"/>
          <Button label="="/>
       </Row>
       
      </Content>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default App;
